thread.title: Arnold Wong

author: Arnold Wong
title: Arnold Wong
text: Recently bought a marble case as a Valentine's gift for my girl friend, the case was perfect for her! The finish was of high quality and looked very stylish on her phone. After a week of using the case we found it to be very protective as well, as my girlfriend is the clumsy type, dropping her phone is a normal occurrence, however this case seem to be holding up well with the 'abuse' from my girlfriend. great shell! 5 stars all round!
